         <abstract>
            <p>We describe an efficient algorithm for the computation of the regulator and a fundamental unit of an arbitrary totally complex quartic order. We analyze its complexity and we present tables with computational results for the orders $\mathbf Z\lbrack\root4 \of {-d}\rbrack, 1 \leqslant d \leqslant 500$.</p>
          </abstract>
